Subject: SCA Fencing Demo
Description: Come learn about fencing done through the Society for Creative Anachronism (SCA)! The SCA is a practical historical group that strives to learn about and recreate the arts and sciences of pre-17th century life. Learn how to fence with one sword, two swords, bucklers, cloaks, and more!  Speakers include:Kell Carnahan - Track: Action Adventure  - Duration: 1 hour and 50 minutes - Audio/video needs: none
